WEBVTT

00:12:58.292 --> 00:13:00.934
where a group of women
were dancing with abandon.

00:13:00.958 --> 00:13:06.268
I jumped in and found myself lost
in the rhythm and the color and the smiles

00:13:06.292 --> 00:13:09.601
and suddenly I realized:

00:13:09.625 --> 00:13:12.708
this is what we do as human beings.

00:13:13.833 --> 00:13:15.184
When we're broken,

00:13:15.208 --> 00:13:19.434
when we feel that we are failing
or are in despair,

00:13:19.458 --> 00:13:21.018
we dance.

00:13:21.042 --> 00:13:22.726
We sing.

00:13:22.750 --> 00:13:24.042
We pray.

00:13:24.833 --> 00:13:29.101
Beauty resides too in showing up,

00:13:29.125 --> 00:13:30.851
in paying attention,